eventrule.label: 一型糖尿病诊断规则
eventrule.name: wen_zhen_fa_xian_tang_niao_bing_zheng_zhuang
eventrule.description: 糖尿病症状 == {'烦渴','多尿','体重减轻'}

eventrule.label: 二型糖尿病诊断规则
eventrule.name: fa_xian_er_lian_tang_niao_bing_zheng_zhuang_qie_xue_tang_chao_biao
eventrule.description: 症状 == {‘烦渴’,‘多尿’} and 空腹血糖 >= 7.0 or 症状 == {'烦渴','皮肤感染'}  空腹血糖 >= 7.0 or 症状 == {'多尿','皮肤感染'} and 空腹血糖 >= 7.0
eventrule.expression: len({'烦渴','多尿','皮肤感染'}.intersection(relatedfield_symptom_list)) >= 2 and numberfield_kong_fu_xue_tang >= 7.0

eventrule.label: 糖尿病酮中毒诊断规则
eventrule.name: tang_niao_bing_tong_zhong_du_zhen_duan_gui_ze
eventrule.description: 症状 == {'昏睡','呕吐','腹痛'} and 疾病名称 in {'非胰岛素依赖糖尿病','胰岛素依赖糖尿病'} and 尿酮体 == ''阳性''
eventrule.expression: len({'昏睡','呕吐','腹痛'}.intersection(relatedfield_symptom_list))==3 and len({'非胰岛素依赖糖尿病','胰岛素依赖糖尿病'}.intersection(relatedfield_disease_name))==1 and len({'阳性'}.intersection(boolfield_tong_ti))==1

eventrule.label: 高血糖诊断规则
eventrule.name: gao_xue_tang_zhen_duan_gui_ze
eventrule.description: 症状 == ''疲乏'' and 疾病名称 in {'非胰岛素依赖糖尿病','胰岛素依赖糖尿病'}
eventrule.expression: len({'疲乏'}.intersection(relatedfield_symptom_list))==1 and len({'非胰岛素依赖糖尿病','胰岛素依赖糖尿病'}.intersection(relatedfield_disease_name))==1

eventrule.label: 糖尿病肾病诊断规则
eventrule.name: tang_niao_bing_shen_bing_zhen_duan_gui_ze
eventrule.description: 疾病名称 in {'非胰岛素依赖糖尿','胰岛素依赖糖尿病'} and 尿微量白蛋白 > 20
eventrule.expression: len({'非胰岛素依赖糖尿','胰岛素依赖糖尿病'}.intersection(relatedfield_disease_name))==1 and A3501>20

eventrule.label: 糖尿病血管病变周围神经炎诊断规则
eventrule.name: tang_niao_bing_xue_guan_bing_bian_zhou_wei_shen_jing_yan_zhen_duan_gui_ze
eventrule.description: 疾病名称 in {'非胰岛素依赖糖尿病', '胰岛素依赖糖尿病'} and 症状 == '’足痛‘'
eventrule.expression: len({'非胰岛素依赖糖尿','胰岛素依赖糖尿病'}.intersection(relatedfield_disease_name))==1 and len({'足痛'}.intersection(relatedfield_symptom_list))==1

eventrule.label: 一项糖尿病症状
eventrule.name: yi_xiang_tang_niao_bing_zheng_zhuang
eventrule.description: 症状 in {'烦渴','多尿','多食','乏力','体重减轻','体重增加','皮肤感染'}
eventrule.expression: len({'烦渴','多尿','多食','乏力','体重减轻','体重增加','皮肤感染'}.intersection(relatedfield_symptom_list)) == 1

eventrule.label: 两项糖尿病症状
eventrule.name: liang_xiang_tang_niao_bing_zheng_zhuang
eventrule.description: 症状 == {'烦渴','多尿'} or 症状 == {'烦渴','体重增加'} or 症状 == {'多尿','皮肤感染'} or 症状 == {'烦渴','皮肤感染'}
eventrule.expression: len({'烦渴','多尿','体重增加','皮肤感染'}.intersection(relatedfield_symptom_list)) >= 2

eventrule.label: 糖化血红蛋白超出正常值
eventrule.name: tang_hua_xue_hong_dan_bai_chao_chu_zheng_chang_zhi

eventrule.label: 糖尿病不适用药品规则
eventrule.name: tang_niao_bing_bu_shi_yong_yao_pin_gui_ze
eventrule.description: 疾病名称 in {'非胰岛素依赖糖尿病','胰岛素依赖糖尿病'} and 药品名称 == {'5%葡萄糖注射液','止咳糖浆'}
eventrule.expression: len({'非胰岛素依赖糖尿病','胰岛素依赖糖尿病'}.intersection(relatedfield_disease_name))==1 and len({'5%葡萄糖注射液','止咳糖浆'}.intersection(relatedfield_drug_name))==1

eventrule.label: 糖尿病监测评估控制不稳定
eventrule.name: tang_niao_bing_jian_ce_ping_gu_bu_wen_ding
eventrule.description: 糖尿病控制效果评估 == ''血糖控制不稳定''

eventrule.label: 糖尿病监测评估控制稳定
eventrule.name: tang_niao_bing_jian_ce_ping_gu_kong_zhi_wen_ding
eventrule.description: 糖尿病控制效果评估 == ''血糖控制稳定''
